                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                    <locus from="5r"/>
                     <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7144MFTabiban">Maṣḥafa falāsfā ṭabibān</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                    <note>The text is not divided into chapters. It agrees with the excerpts published in
                      <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/8VCRF6G8"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Cornill1875Falasfa"/><title level="m">Maṣḥafa Falâsfâ Ṭabîbân. Das Buch der weisen Philosophen nach dem aethiopischen untersucht</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Carl Heinrich</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Cornill</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Leipzig</pubPlace><publisher>Druck von F. A. Brockhaus</publisher><date>1875</date><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/MashafaFalsafaTabibanDasBuchDerWeisenPhilosophen</note></bibl> and
                      <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/TQ2NBVAC"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Dillmann1866Chrestomathia"/><title level="m">Chrestomathia Aethiopica edita et glossario explanata</title><editor><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Christian Friedrich August</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Dillmann</t:surname></editor><pubPlace>Lipsiae</pubPlace><publisher>T. O. Weigel</publisher><date>1866</date><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_V2XoxZmczckC</note><citedRange unit="page">40–45</citedRange></bibl>,
                       its readings agree partly with <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/FSUor16">Frankfurt, Universitätsbibliothek Johann Christian Senckenberg, Frankfurt Ms. or. 16</ref> and partly with <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/UBTaeth6">Tübingen, Universitätsbibliothek Tübingen, Tübingen Aeth. 6</ref>.
                      However, in the introduction this manuscript, <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet158#ms_i1">Paris, Bibliothèque nationale de France, BnF Éthiopien 158: Maṣḥafa falāsfā ṭabibān (in ms_i1)</ref> and <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet159#ms_i1">Paris, Bibliothèque nationale de France, BnF Éthiopien 159: Maṣḥafa falāsfā ṭabibān (in ms_i1)</ref> have
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምስጢራተ፡</foreign> instead of   <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምስጢራቲሃ፡</foreign>, see  <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/8VCRF6G8"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Cornill1875Falasfa"/><title level="m">Maṣḥafa Falâsfâ Ṭabîbân. Das Buch der weisen Philosophen nach dem aethiopischen untersucht</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Carl Heinrich</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Cornill</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Leipzig</pubPlace><publisher>Druck von F. A. Brockhaus</publisher><date>1875</date><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/MashafaFalsafaTabibanDasBuchDerWeisenPhilosophen</note><citedRange unit="page">36</citedRange><citedRange unit="line">9</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                    <note>On <locus target="#12ra"/>, there is a sentence attributed to the author of the work.</note>

                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                       በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ መሓሪ፡
                       ወመስተሣህል፡ ወላዕሌሁ፡ ትውክልትነ፡ ወረድኤትነ፡ ዘውእቱ፡ ይሁብ፡ መክፈልተ፡ ሀብታት፡ በከመ፡ ፈቀደ፤
                       ውእቱ፡ ይጼጉ፡ ወውእቱ፡ ያስተነቢ፡ ወይሁብ፡ መንፈሶ፡ ለኵሉ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe"/>
                       ንዌጥን፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ በጽሒፈ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ፈላስፋ፡ ጠቢባን፡ ዘተናገሩ፡ ባቲ፡ ለለ፡ ፩፡
                       እምኔሆሙ፡ በአምጣነ፡ ክሂሎቱ፤
                    </incipit>
                     
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        <locus from="5v"/>
                      ይቤ፡ ጠቢብ፡ ወሬዛ፡ ጠቢብ፡ ይኄይስ፡ እምነ፡ አረጋዊ፡ አብድ። <hi rend="rubric">ተብህለ፡</hi> እስመ፡ ተግሣጽሰ፡ ይከብር፡ እምነ፡ አዕናቍ፡ ክቡራት፡
                      ወያከብር፡ ዘመደ፡ ኅሡራን፡ ወያቀውሞሙ፡ ውስተ፡ ምቅዋመ፡ ክቡራን፡ ወያከብር፡ እንበለ፡ ተባይጾ፡ ወያብዝኅ፡ ረድኤተ፡ እንዘ፡ አልቦቱ፡ ዘርእ። <hi rend="rubric">ተብህለ፡</hi>
                      እስመ፡ ጥበብሰ፡ ይጸንዕ፡ እምነ፡ ዘመድ፡ ብዙኃን፡ ወአእምሮሂ፡ ይከብር፡ እምነ፡ ዘመድ፡ ክቡራን። <hi rend="rubric">ተብህለ፡</hi> ግዕዝ፡ ሠናይ፡ ይኄይስ፡
                      እምነ፡ ቢጽ፡ ሠናይ፡ ወመጽሐፍሂ፡ ናዛዚሁ፡ ለትኩዝ፡ ውእቱ። <hi rend="rubric">ተብህለ፡</hi> ሕስዋ፡ ለጥበብ፡ እስመ፡ ይእቲ፡ ተውሳከ፡ ልቡና፡ ወመራኂተ፡
                      ፍኖት፡ ይእቲ፡ ወዓርክ፡ ይእቲ፡ በውስተ፡ ተአንግዶ፡ ወሞገስ፡ ይእቲ፡ በውስተ፡ ጉባኤ። <hi rend="rubric">ተብህለ፡</hi> መቅድመ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዘይፈቅድ፡ ባቲ፡
                      ሰብእ፡ ልቡና፡ ወተግሣጽ፡ ወጽድቅ፡ ወትዕግሥት፡ ወጥበብ፡ ወንጽሕና፡ ወተገድሎ፡ ወአእኵቶ፡ ወጸልዮ፡ ጸሎታት፡ እንተ፡ ይእቲ፡ መሠረተ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ዘታበጽሕ፡ ኀበ፡
                      ፈጣሪ፡ ሎቱ፡ ስብሐት። ወጽድቀ፡ ቃል፡ ወዜና፡ ወርኂቅ፡ እመሐላ፡ በሐሰት፡ ወተቀብሎ፡ በገጽ፡ ፍሡሕ፤ ወአክብሮ፡ አናግድ፡ ወአሠንዮ፡ ለኵሉ፡ ወዓዊበ፡ ጎር፡</incipit>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="25r"/>
                     <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1914Mashaf">በስመ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe"/>
                  ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘአቡነ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS2209Athanasi">አትናሲስ፡ ሊቀ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ዘእስክንድርያ፡</persName> ወዘአንቲያኮስ፤ በእንተ፡ ተኀሥሦ፡ ቃላት፡
                ዘውስተ፡ መጻሕፍት።</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <note>The questions are not numbered.</note>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <locus from="31v" to="33r"/>
                     <title type="incomplete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2133OntheL">ድርሳን፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ወብፁዕ፡
                ዮሐንስ፡ አፈ፡ ወርቅ፡ ትርጓሜሁ፡ ለአቡነ፡ ዘበሰማያት።</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ናሁ፡ ጸሎቶሙ፡ ለሰብእ፡ ዘዘዚአሁ፡ ውእቱ፡ ከመ፡ ሐረዩ፡ ለርእሶሙ፡ ለሊሆሙ፡ እንዘ፡
                ይመስሎሙ፡ ዘይሔይሶሙ፡ ለርእሶሙ፡ እስመቦ፡ እምኔሆሙ፡ ዘይቀውም፡ ውስተ፡ ጸሎት።</incipit>
                     <note>The copying of the text was not finished.</note>
