      <t:body>
         <t:div type="edition">

            <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="SentencePlato" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet157#ms_i3">
               <t:note xml:lang="en">Cp.  <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet159#SentencePlato">Paris, Bibliothèque nationale de France, BnF Éthiopien 159: No item: , could not check for ms_i1.2</t:ref>.</t:note>
               <t:ab>
                  <t:pb n="6r"/><cb n="a"/>
         ይቤልዎ፡ ለአፍላጦን፡ ለምንትኑ፡ ኢያስተጋባእከ፡ ጥበበ፡ ወንዋየ፤ ይቤ፡ ለእዘዘ፡ ፍጻሜ።
       </t:ab>
            </t:div>

            <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="SentenceTranslator" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet157#ms_i3">
               <t:note xml:lang="en">A sentence added by the Arabic translator.</t:note>
               <t:ab>
                  <t:pb n="14r"/><cb n="a"/>
         ይቤ፡ አውጻኢሃ፡ ለዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ፬፡ ግብር፡ ይዌስኩ፡ ልቡና፤ ዘውእቶሙ፡ መብልዕ፡ ሠናይ፤ ወጼና፡ ምዑዝ፤ ወነጽሮ፡ መልክዕ፡ ሠናይ፤
         ወተናግሮ፡ ምስለ፡ ጠቢብ፡ ወማእምር፤ ወ፬ሂ፡ ግብር፡ ያማስኑ፡ አእምሮተ፤ ዘውእቶሙ፡ መብልዕ፡ ሕሱም፤ ወነጽሮ፡ መልክዕ፡ ሕሱም፤
         ወተናግሮ፡ ምስለ፡ አብድ፤ ወአጼንዎ፡ ጼና፡ ፍጉገ።
       </t:ab>
            </t:div>

            <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Question62" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet157#ms_i4">
               <t:note xml:lang="en">The Gǝʿǝz varies from the Greek version.</t:note>
               <t:ab>
         ይቤ፡ <hi rend="rubric">አንት</hi>፤ እፎ፡ ርእየ፡ ሙሴ፡ አፃብዒሁ፡ ለእግዚእ፡ ልዑል፡ እምቅድመ፡ ይሠገው፡ ወይትመሰል፡ ከመ፡ ሰብእ።
         አውሥአ፡ <hi rend="rubric">አትና</hi>፡ ወይቤ፤ ዘርእየ፡ ሙሴ፡ እዴሁ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ አርአያ፡ ለትስብእቱ፤ ወሶበ፡ ርእየ፡ ሙሴ፡ ጸሐፈ፡ እንዘ፡ ይብል፡
         <t:gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe"/>
               </t:ab>
            </t:div>

            <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Answer68" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet157#ms_i4">
               <t:note xml:lang="en">The Gǝʿǝz is more complete than the Greek version.</t:note>
               <t:ab>
                  <t:pb n="26r"/><cb n="b"/>
                  <t:gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe"/>
         አልቦ፡ እስመ፡ ቅድስት፡ ጥምቀት፡ አንጽሐቶሙ፡
       </t:ab>
            </t:div>
         </t:div>
      </t:body>
  </t:text></TEI>